msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2焊盘参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:218
msgid "**颜色范围（Pad）**：为“焊盘”区域配置有效的 HSV 颜色范围。"
msgstr ""

